{"tid":2334310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"請夏結束隔離返家　將持續暫停活動","createTime":"2020-12-21T05:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T06:00:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbf6444fd9040811cb3c9036d35c885f3ed17bc","tid":2334310,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"從本月 7 日確診肺炎至今，屬於無症狀患者的請夏便中斷了活動，不得不缺席各種年末頒獎典禮。隨著隔離解除，經紀公司也透露了她接下來的活動！<br />\n<br />\nMNH Entertainment 今天（21 日）在請夏的官方 Fan cafe 上宣布，她於 12 月 7 日起至 18 日間都待在生活治療中心接受治療，由於屬於無症狀患者，根據韓國政府的規定，請夏於 18 日當天由醫生判斷「沒有傳染力」後，便解除隔離狀態並返家休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0fd5caa9389974ab537c93e5b1f372c4/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-21/132462-889760.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0fd5caa9389974ab537c93e5b1f372c4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-21%2F132462-889760.png&h=c6746a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「由於近期疫情益發嚴重，請夏依然將暫停官方活動，專注於保持健康和安全。」MNH Entertainment 表示：「本公司未來也會徹底遵照保健當局的防疫方針，視旗下藝人和工作人員的健康、安全為優先要務。」<br />\n<br />\n在這之前，請夏已宣布原定於 12 月 10 日發行的先行曲 &ldquo;X&rdquo;，以及將於 2021 年 1 月 4 日問世的首張正規專輯〈Querencia〉都會延後公開。在她重啟活動前，只好先用她今年發表的多首新歌度過這段時間囉！"},{"pid":"bc93e1cb0a4f7c0a445ff4f664195d69cfb4915f","tid":2334310,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"好好休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1e7ea655b5f20cede5f949328fec903f3461b8","tid":2334310,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"慢慢休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0162862f2fb0a7e1efa707a4002b7396de9ca4f6","tid":2334310,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c1e7ea655b5f20cede5f949328fec903f3461b8","tid":2334310,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"慢慢休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}